Usage: get_analysis_view [-help] <view_Name> {-constraint_mode | -delay_corner }

-help                # Prints out the command usage
<view_Name>          # Name of the analysis view to query (string, required)
-constraint_mode     # Returns the constraint mode associated with the
                     # specified analysis view (bool, optional)
-delay_corner        # Returns the delay calculation corner associated with the
                     # specified analysis view (bool, optional)